                  </persName>
             sworn. - I assisted in stopping the prisoner; he had a pewter bason, and some leaden pipe. (Produces them.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner did not say any thing in his defence, but called one witness, who gave him a good character. <rs id="t18030914-42-verdict251" type="verdictDescription">
